{"tid":2011980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[收返專營權未]吉野家上環分店欠租5個月　業主入稟追討6.5萬元 (18:44)","createTime":"2020-05-11T11:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T11:34:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f6f0957a327215c1731d7102577951e64423a4","tid":2011980,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"連鎖日式快餐店吉野家近半年來多家分店先後結業，其位於上環金龍中心的分店拖欠5個月租金，遭業主入稟區域法院追討，涉款近6.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n原告為Wichita Investment Ltd.，被告為Yoshinoya（GNC）Ltd.，而被追討欠租的吉野家分店位於中環德輔道中188號金龍中心地下1、2及6號舖。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指出，吉野家從2017年3月起以月租27.6萬元租用上址，並繳交合共逾100萬元按金，為期3年。惟吉野家自去年11月起開始拖欠部分租金及管理費，直至今年3月共拖欠款項約100萬元，扣除已繳付的按金後，尚欠款項約6.5萬元。原告多次嘗試追討不果後，遂入稟追討。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200511/s00001/1589192099815/%e5%90%89%e9%87%8e%e5%ae%b6%e4%b8%8a%e7%92%b0%e5%88%86%e5%ba%97%e6%ac%a0%e7%a7%9f5%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88-%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e5%85%a5%e7%a8%9f%e8%bf%bd%e8%a8%8e6-5%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200511%2Fs00001%2F1589192099815%2F%25e5%2590%2589%25e9%2587%258e%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e4%25b8%258a%25e7%2592%25b0%25e5%2588%2586%25e5%25ba%2597%25e6%25ac%25a0%25e7%25a7%259f5%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%259c%2588-%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%2585%25a5%25e7%25a8%259f%25e8%25bf%25bd%25e8%25a8%258e6-5%25e8%2590%25ac%25e5%2585%2583&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=816940d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200511%2Fs00001%2F1589192099815%2F%25e5%2590%2589%25e9%2587%258e%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e4%25b8%258a%25e7%2592%25b0%25e5%2588%2586%25e5%25ba%2597%25e6%25ac%25a0%25e7%25a7%259f5%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%259c%2588-%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%2585%25a5%25e7%25a8%259f%25e8%25bf%25bd%25e8%25a8%258e6-5%25e8%2590%25ac%25e5%2585%2583&h=6cab1d93\" data-auto-link target=